  "compactCustomInstructions": "After compaction, immediately re-read plans/active-context.md before doing anything else \u2014 it is the authoritative resume point. Do not waste summary tokens on content already captured in plans/ files (active-context.md, decisions.md, progress.md) \u2014 those files persist on disk and will be re-read. Focus the summary on: in-flight tool call results not yet written to disk, ephemeral error messages, and any decisions made verbally that have not been recorded. Always preserve: current branch name, uncommitted file list, active plan file path, and the exact task being worked on at the moment of compaction.",
